<item>
            <title>[AMQ-1363] activemq/conf/log4j.properties does not seem to get recognized</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-1363</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Try taking a binary build; enabling debug logging by editing activemq/conf/log4j.properties, then rerunning the broker. I get no change!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;BTW I&apos;ve patched the activemq-core-*-tests.jar to not include a log4j.properties file. Also I tried adding the activemq/conf directory explicitly in the console - to no avail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also tried zapping the activeio jars and grepping the jars to see if any had any included log4j.properties files - to no avail&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
